  "monster": {
    "title": "Soyl Qoll.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Soyl Qoll has a spiked green body and snakes for hair. It looks diseased.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 320     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ ++  </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++        </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ∞       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><darkgrey>rElec: .        </darkgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 160% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 86% to hit with the +9 demon whip of the Harvest.\nIt has about 77% to hit you.\n\nAttack                Max Damage      \nHit: antimagic touch  43 + antimagic  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt is vulnerable to silver and hated by Zin.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Fast:<lightgrey>\n   This creature moves and acts 50% faster.\n\n<white>Covering ground quickly:<lightgrey>\n   This creature moves slightly faster.\n\n<white>Sheltered from injuries:<lightgrey>\n   Half of the damage suffered by this creature is redirected to the ally\n   protecting it instead.\n\n<white>Doubled in vigour:<lightgrey>\n   This monster's current and maximum health are temporarily doubled.\n\n<white>Weak-willed:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's willpower is reduced by half.\n\n",
    "spellset": [
